So much I've learned
through my childhood, which

00:00:26.770 --> 00:00:28.510
I've lived kind of
a unique childhood

00:00:28.510 --> 00:00:33.220
with epilepsy, which has been
kind of from five years old

00:00:33.220 --> 00:00:35.320
till about 13.

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:37.690
And of course, one
of those unexpected

00:00:37.690 --> 00:00:43.970
