to sponsor someone in their mid

00:03:53.500 --> 00:03:59.050
20s to compete because the 19-,
15-year-old is going to beat me

00:03:59.050 --> 00:04:00.070
out.

00:04:00.070 --> 00:04:02.590
So it was up to me, if I
wanted to stay in snowboarding,

00:04:02.590 --> 00:04:07.160
to recreate myself, reinvent
who I was in the sport.

00:04:07.160 --> 00:04:11.230
And so the self-portrait
world became my focus

00:04:11.230 --> 00:04:15.070
and gave me a whole other
15 years as a career.

00:04:15.070 --> 00:04:16.870
I'm 45 years old now.

00:04:16.870 --> 00:04:20.589
I still have sponsors as a
snowboarding professional,

00:04:20.589 --> 00:04:25.240
and it's really
based on creativity.

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:29.020
And that space of
creativity has changed

00:04:29.020 --> 00:04:32.110
over the 15 years I've
been doing self portraits,

00:04:32.110 --> 00:04:34.720
