Not everything does
that I do, so I

00:17:03.540 --> 00:17:05.640
don't have a strong
connection with it

00:17:05.640 --> 00:17:07.589
and I'll move on to
something that is.

00:17:07.589 --> 00:17:11.430
And what I've
learned why that is,

00:17:11.430 --> 00:17:14.790
at least from my perspective,
is that we're all

00:17:14.790 --> 00:17:17.760
born with something first.

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:21.270
The first organ that's
formed is the heart.

00:17:21.270 --> 00:17:22.670
That's kind of what takes place.

00:17:22.670 --> 00:17:24.990
It's our main seed.

00:17:24.990 --> 00:17:27.329
And that was the
one thing that I

00:17:27.329 --> 00:17:32.010
keep going back to for all my
answers that I can't answer.

00:17:32.010 --> 00:17:35.010
And that's the one
thing somewhere

00:17:35.010 --> 00:17:39.690
in me is knowing
what to do with it

00:17:39.690 --> 00:17:45.870
and back to resonating by
doing something in action.

00:17:45.870 --> 00:17:50.670
And I'd love to talk to you
all about what resonates.

00:17:50.670 --> 00:17:52.250
I know snowboarding has for me.

00:17:52.250 --> 00:17:56.120
Living off the grid, being
closer to the indigenous

00:17:56.120 --> 00:17:59.090
needs of what we
need to live life.

00:17:59.090 --> 00:18:02.300
