imagine if you do

00:18:16.790 --> 00:18:19.010
that, you have some
sort of exhilaration

00:18:19.010 --> 00:18:21.680
like you just ran a marathon
and all you have to do

00:18:21.680 --> 00:18:25.100
is brush your
teeth to feel that.

00:18:25.100 --> 00:18:29.630
