connected with what we do,

00:18:29.630 --> 00:18:32.570
what we use.

00:18:32.570 --> 00:18:37.100
And again, it's not
the same for everybody.

00:18:37.100 --> 00:18:39.840
It's really what
resonates in the heart

00:18:39.840 --> 00:18:41.780
because that's kind
of, really, that's

00:18:41.780 --> 00:18:44.110
all we have to lean back on.

