in Alaska, I was like,

00:19:39.170 --> 00:19:42.100
what kind of shape
does this house

00:19:42.100 --> 00:19:45.190
that I'm going to build, this
dream, what kind of shape

00:19:45.190 --> 00:19:47.320
does it have?

00:19:47.320 --> 00:19:50.740
