you've got to really let

00:19:50.740 --> 00:19:54.400
go of all your ideas,
close your eyes,

00:19:54.400 --> 00:19:58.470
and like, what's
this really about?

00:19:58.470 --> 00:20:03.925
And I started to realize
it was about me, my heart.

00:20:03.925 --> 00:20:09.850
And it was like, where does
this experience of feeling

00:20:09.850 --> 00:20:10.930
most alive--

00:20:10.930 --> 00:20:13.600
where does this live?

00:20:13.600 --> 00:20:17.470
I started to realize this was
standing on a mountain peak.

00:20:17.470 --> 00:20:19.820
This is where, in
the past 33 years,

00:20:19.820 --> 00:20:23.870
this is where I've
felt most alive.

00:20:23.870 --> 00:20:27.220
I started looking at all these
photos and I'm like, wow.

00:20:27.220 --> 00:20:30.500
There's a shape to this feeling,
standing on a mountain peak

00:20:30.500 --> 00:20:33.060
and reaching out to the world.

00:20:33.060 --> 00:20:36.370
This is the start of
an idea, off a feeling.

00:20:36.370 --> 00:20:38.360
And I think everyone
can relate this feeling.

00:20:38.360 --> 00:20:41.720
It's just where you're high
on life and feel most alive.

00:20:41.720 --> 00:20:44.210
Like, everyone has
that certain structure,

00:20:44.210 --> 00:20:48.450
just reaching out as well,
keeping your feet grounded.

00:20:48.450 --> 00:20:52.205
And from there on, it just
started to take shape.

00:20:52.205 --> 00:20:56.710
I'm like, oh, I've
got to draw this down.

00:20:56.710 --> 00:20:59.650
And soon as I knew
it, I was experiencing

00:20:59.650 --> 00:21:03.310
something that's been
experienced for hundreds

00:21:03.310 --> 00:21:04.780
and hundreds of years.

00:21:04.780 --> 00:21:09.280
You see this drawing of a star
connecting to all your dots

00:21:09.280 --> 00:21:10.990
on your body.

00:21:10.990 --> 00:21:12.615
And if you connect
them the other way,

00:21:12.615 --> 00:21:15.520
it becomes a pentagon.

00:21:15.520 --> 00:21:18.930
So I think if you
go off of instinct

00:21:18.930 --> 00:21:21.300
or you go off the
golden ratio, you're

00:21:21.300 --> 00:21:23.550
going to end up
with the same thing.

00:21:23.550 --> 00:21:25.650
Of course, you have to
really let go and listen

00:21:25.650 --> 00:21:30.160
to that heartbeat.

00:21:30.160 --> 00:21:34.130
Go where, where does that
heartbeat feel most alive?

00:21:34.130 --> 00:21:37.490
For me it was staying
on the mountain, where

00:21:37.490 --> 00:21:40.910
I realized that's what I want
my house to be because that's

00:21:40.910 --> 00:21:42.538
where I felt most alive.

