MIKE BASICH: So
that was my project

00:24:10.360 --> 00:24:13.310
of finding my
place in the world.

00:24:13.310 --> 00:24:17.410
And what I've learned, which
the biggest part I learned

00:24:17.410 --> 00:24:20.290
